metadata.name: SYNTHIA #1/17
metadata.description:
In the first 30 minutes of Transmutations being live, FAN3 Communi3 membership holders can purchase SYNTHIA at a reduced special price of $40. After 30 minutes SYNTHIA can be purchased for $80.

Collectors of SYNTHIA will receive a special reward of discounted prices in Giusy Amoroso's next Nifty Gateway drop.
